{"tid":744960,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【魔女之條件？】有村架純新劇演教師戀中三學生","createTime":"2018-07-16T10:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T01:03:50.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3989ac1796899b18ef3e8a0493920e6057b145d4","tid":744960,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"25歲日本女星有村架純落實演出TBS電視台10月首播新劇，首次挑戰演老師角色。劇集係改編自漫畫《中學聖日記》，有村架純飾演嘅末永聖，係一位女教師，有一位於海外生活嘅未婚夫，但卻與年輕10年、只得15歲嘅美少年學生黑岩晶，展開一段世俗唔容許嘅愛情，題材大膽，故事有啲似松嶋菜菜子與瀧澤秀明合作經典日劇《魔女之條件》。劇集將於本月底開鏡，前半部會根據原著漫畫，後半部會係全新創作嘅劇本，而邊個演出靚仔學生仍有待公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180716&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58448391\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180716%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58448391&d=aHUqRSLuF0LVJnrkA1twt7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f605d152\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180716%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58448391&h=e146692f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180716&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58448391</a>"},{"pid":"a1752122f1eee05ebcdbecccaac46d2e1d913220","tid":744960,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T13:17:16.000Z","msg":"係咪塊面好大果條女?"},{"pid":"3dfe8c0a909caf58c3f91a5a057c5fff949188f9","tid":744960,"uid":115238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1752122f1eee05ebcdbecccaac46d2e1d913220","tid":744960,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T13:17:16.000Z","msg":"係咪塊面好大果條女?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"水腫姐<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/003716_f109be16dcff45c782184863af670d77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F003716_f109be16dcff45c782184863af670d77.jpg&h=2da002c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.img